// DWD = German Weather Service
Deutscher Wetterdienst DWD - Topic of the day Weather maps DWD - weather encyclopedia Forecast Satellite view Web search Rain forecast
The weather forecast for your preferred state (Germany only). Displays the rain (or film of the last hours) radar over Germany. Every day an other interesting thema concerning the actual weather. The weather encyclopedia from the DWD (German Weather Service). Available are several (forecast) weather cards from Europe and the world. Actual and past satellite pictures from all over the world. Startpage: a secure privacy friendly search page.
